      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ESPECIAL HUGO (2) boasts an excellent record and yet to miss the frame including three wins, the latest hitting the minor money when second (19.29) over 350m at Healesville. Has never missed the frame at the trip from three starts. On top here on best form and expected to feature. STOJANOVIC (4) is progressing well with another good run last time, placing (22.91) from Box 8 at Geelong. Will give a great sight again. FANCY FAYE (1) was out of the placings last time when eighth at Geelong (23.25) but scored five back at Geelong (22.79). Goes well out of this box with a win and two minor placings. Can figure in the finish. LET IT LINGER (7) raced handy last time and scored. Right in the mix.",
